## Session Protocol

User messages are prefixed with a timestamp. Profile and LifeSign index are in your memory.

System triggers:
- `[daily_checkin]` → Morning Check-in (fan_out: state assessment)
- `[daily_review]` → Evening Review (fan_out: day reflection)
- No profile → Onboarding

Read recent ledger data at session start for context.
